text: Munxar Falcons F.C. is a Maltese football club from the village of Munxar, Gozo, Malta. They were founded in 1972 and they are currently playing in the Gozo Football League Second Division. == Honors == * Gozo Football League Second Division : Winners (2): 1990/91 2017/2018 : Runners-up (2): 1987/1988, 1988/1989 * Adidas cup : Winners (1): 1976/1977 * Knock Out Second Division : Winners (5): 1978/1979, 1983/1984, 1990/1991, 2016/2017, 2017/2018 : Runners- up (3): 1980/1981, 1999/2000, 2011/2012 * Cup of good repute : Winners (3): 1993/1994, 2008/2009, 2009/2010 ==References== == External links == * Official Account on Facebook * Munxar Falcons Official Website Category:Football clubs in Malta Category:Association football clubs established in 1972 Category:1972 establishments in Malta Category:Munxar
title: Munxar Falcons F.C.
